4OhgSqPjoq6H1VPpg">Sài môn - 柴門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Thi%C3%AAn-M%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-zL1WjWsx954wTVcqqmOLTA">Tặng Thiên Mụ tự hoà thượng - 贈天姥寺和尚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-tVCgetl94ylIpxXT-wJP2g">Phan Quế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%A2u-ki%E1%BA%BFn-s%E1%BA%AFc-m%E1%BB%A5c-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-tam-C%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A5-t%C6%B0-ngh%E1%BB%8B-lang-T%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%A9-Di%E1%BB%87u-tr%E1%BB%AB-gi%C3%A1m-s%C3%A1t-d%E1%BB%AF-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BB%91-vi%E1%BB%85n-h%E1%BB%89/poem-MckcrDzR5IMVz8q99e9tfA">Tần Châu kiến sắc mục Tiết tam Cứ thụ tư nghị lang, Tất tứ Diệu trừ giám sát, dữ nhị tử hữu cố viễn, hỉ thiên quan kiêm thuật tác cư, hoàn tam thập vận - 秦州見敕目薛三璩授司議郎畢四曜除監察與二子有故遠喜遷官兼述 索居凡三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khang-H%E1%BB%AFu-Vi/Thu-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Vi%E1%BB%87t-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-VT07ZdK2UWhuOZKjpf-nYw">Thu đăng Việt Vương đài - 秋登越王臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khang-H%E1%BB%AFu-Vi/author-aDG80DQVg9ATdlqFPVMW7g">Khang Hữu Vi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%C4%A9nh-S%C4%A9/Tr%C3%B9ng-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%93i-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%E1%BB%97-S%C6%A1n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-T%C3%BA-%C4%91%C4%83ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-th%C3%A0nh-ch%C3%BAc-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-t%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%85-nh%C3%A2n-d%C4%A9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-WnLFYoHrATCUGWk-sq_sZw">Trùng dương nhật bồi Nguyên Lỗ Sơn Đức Tú đăng bắc thành, chúc đối tân tễ, nhân dĩ tặng biệt - 重陽日陪元魯山德秀登北城，矚對新霽，因以贈別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%C4%A9nh-S%C4%A9/author-WabbZrtUKpM6RTDqjMeaIA">Tiêu Dĩnh Sĩ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
